Notes:
. Vélez Sarsfield played as runner-up of Nacional championship 1985.
. 6 teams from Interior tournament.
. 5 teams from Primera División championship.
. Argentinos Juniors can not play because it was qualified to play Libertadores
  cup as holders.
. Final: Boca Juniors won by goal difference (4-3).
